movies with my dad.

03:14.440 --> 03:16.317
We ate Chinese food
and Buffalo wings.

03:16.480 --> 03:18.755
Dad fell asleep during
<i>The Spy Who Shagged</i> Me...

03:18.920 --> 03:21.878
